## 🔑 Important Files to Update

### ⚠️ appsettings.json
**WAJIB UPDATE dengan credentials database kamu:**

Dari:
```json
{
"ConnectionStrings": {
    "DefaultConnection": "Host=localhost;Port=5432;Database=prodev_db;Username=postgres;Password=YOUR_PASSWORD_HERE"
  }
}
```

Menjadi (dengan password kamu):
```json
{
  "ConnectionStrings": {
    "DefaultConnection": "Host=localhost;Port=5432;Database=prodev_db;Username=postgres;Password=passwordmu123"
  }
}
```

